Seller is Offering $ 8000.00 in Concessions to be used at Buyer's Discretion:
Come see this 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath plus a Bonus room in Highland Forest S/D.  Master Bedroom has 2 separate closets, Kitchen has a double door pantry.  HVAC is approximately 10 years old, Electric Water Heater is Approximately 4 years old.
NO HOA, Close to shopping and Schools.  
Fenced in back yard with a Storage Building.
Don't wait, schedule your showing today!!
